manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "dm885_auth_service"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "dm885_auth_service"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
build = "build.rs"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
actix-rt = "2.7.0"
actix-utils = "3.0.1"
actix-web = "4.2.1"
actix-web-httpauth = "0.8.0"
color-eyre = "0.6.2"
colored = "2.0.0"
config = "0.13.2"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
eyre = "0.6.8"
futures-util = "0.3.25"
jsonwebtoken = "8.1.1"
regex = "1.7.0"
tracing = "0.1.37"
tracing-futures = "0.2.5"

[dependencies.argon2]
version = "0.4.1"
features = ["parallel"]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.23"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.147"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6.2"
features = ["runtime-actix-native-tls", "postgres", "macros", "uuid", "chrono"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.tracing-log]
version = "0.1.3"
features = ["env_logger"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["fmt", "env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.2.2"
features = ["serde"]
